				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/B%C3%A1ch-chu-4/poem-XbHO3UnN0cL4ii8no0iGKg">Bách chu 4 - 柏舟 4</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%93i-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-c%C3%B4ng-Thu-v%C3%A3n-b%E1%BA%AFc-tr%C3%AC-l%C3%A2m-di%E1%BB%83u/poem-GCX-ZHe5j-GqZqZFsIpJxw">Bồi Trịnh công “Thu vãn bắc trì lâm diểu” - 陪鄭公秋晚北池臨眺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/C%C3%A1t-c%C3%BA-2/poem-w-SBZQPTSV_LzY0StAT7Dw">Cát cú 2 - 葛屨 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/C%E1%BB%95-phong-k%E1%BB%B3-08-Thi%C3%AAn-t%C3%A2n-tam-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%C3%AC/poem-h4Jd-rpUD9F5lc3rtXZ3WA">Cổ phong kỳ 08 (Thiên tân tam nguyệt thì) - 古風其八（天津三月時）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/H%E1%BA%A1-v%C5%A9/poem-1WwuWOOTnqta5CuA9yU9AQ">Hạ vũ - 賀雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-T%C4%83ng/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-xu%E1%BA%A5t-uy%E1%BB%83n-ch%C3%BAc-m%E1%BB%A5c-%E1%BB%A9ng-l%E1%BB%87nh/poem-irG9NkfctYFjmBvb_gxxLw">Phụng hoạ “Xuân nhật xuất uyển chúc mục” ứng lệnh - 奉和春日出苑矚目應令</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Gi%E1%BA%A3-T%C4%83ng/author-FuHcCAWfmdvOkzOdR9i87g">Giả Tăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-M%E1%BA%A1t-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/Th%E1%BA%ADp-nguy%E1%BB%87t-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-ZdBC1sHVjwm_oYFyqHn8_w">Thập nguyệt cảm hoài thi kỳ 2 - 十月感懷詩其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Qu%C3%A1ch-M%E1%BA%A1t-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3c/author-QwHGtxwbcIXnt9ZJeL8mXw">Quách Mạt Nhược</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90i%E1%BB%83n-Thi%E1%BA%BFt-t%E1%BB%B1-Thi-Ch%C3%A2u-quy/poem-Wtg7pr18QYwpC7wnveu-vw">Trịnh Điển Thiết tự Thi Châu quy - 鄭典設自施州歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/T%E1%BB%B1-Thi%C3%AAn-Ki%E1%BB%87n-h%E1%BB%93i-qu%C3%A1-L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ki%E1%BB%87t-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-wTv176lWZ3zPw4CM8bHKzg">Tự Thiên Kiện hồi quá Lý Thường Kiệt miếu - 自天健回過李常傑廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Vi%E1%BA%BFt-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-KrhE9fPPdxg7MJNECyal4Q">Phạm Viết Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/%E1%BB%A8ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%E1%BB%AD-ch%C6%B0-quan-t%C3%A1c-h%C6%B0ng-bang-b%C3%A0i-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-k%E1%BA%BF/poem-rPiWQUngGNEeg18t8W-z8Q">Ứng thượng sử chư quan tác hưng bang bài ngoại kế - 應上使諸官作興邦排外計</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
